<DD><li><b>ZIP code</b></li>
<li><b>Date of birth</b></li>
<li><b>Type of residence</b> (house, apartment, or mobile home)</li>
<li><b>Veteran status</b></li>
<li><b>Current income and assets from all sources for self, spouse and others in the household</b></li>
<li><b>Estimates of current expenses</b> (such as mortgage/rent, utilities, out-of-pocket medical bills, expenses for caring for someone at home while you work or go to school, etc.)</li>
